channel.title: (FIXED)Need Help With CMD IPCONFIG(FIXED)
channel.description:
I'm not sure if it's because of my new router or what. I once tried making a server here with a modem, the uTorrent way, never worked. So I gave up, I got a router for X-Box Live. I feel like learning this stuff. So I'm right at the beginning of portforwarding, with bad, bad, and bad. I opened cmd(Command Prompt) and as usual, typed in ipconfig, ipconfig , Ipconfig, IPCONFIG, everything, and I would get this.
[img]http://i31.tinypic.com/2hx0j7b.png[/img]
I'm not sure how to fix this, mabye somebody here can PLEASE help me?
I was following this tutorial, mabye because of the changepath and path edited could've caused this? [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,342685.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,342685.0.html[/url]
